                <exercise>
                    <introduction>
                        <p>
                            Now, let's think about the area after <m>n</m> steps, where <m>n</m> is an arbitrary number.
                        </p>
                    </introduction>
                    <task workspace="1in">
                        <statement>
                            <p>
