                    </task>
                    <task workspace="1in">
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                In the previous problem, you may have noticed a pattern in your final answers.  Use this to guess a simple formula for the area after <m>n</m> steps (in other words, simplify so your answer is no longer a sum).
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </task>
                    <task workspace="1in">
                        <statement>
                            <p>
